com.varmateo.yawg.freemarker

Class FreemarkerDataModel.YawgFreemarkerDataModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.varmateo.yawg.freemarker.FreemarkerDataModel.YawgFreemarkerDataModel
  • Enclosing class:
    FreemarkerDataModel

    public static final class FreemarkerDataModel.YawgFreemarkerDataModel
extends Object
    This is a class that provides the right getters in order to have the appropriate template variables visible inside the Freemarker templates.

    The purpose of this Java bean is to provide the template variables named with prefix "yawg.".
